oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Boys with pet deer
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: A photograph of W.C. Burton's boys and their pet deer and dogs on the steps of their home near Norris Dam. The oldest boy is wearing a plaid jacket and appears to have a book in his hand.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Tennessee Department of Conservation Photograph Collection, 1937-1976
